Exmatrikulator Grunt
====================

Frontend files for Exmatrikulator.

Node Installation
-----------------

1. Download source of latest NodeJS version from https://nodejs.org/
2. Extract files, execute configure script, then compile it with make and
   finally use make install


Install grunt client
--------------------

To install grunt invoke the following command:

	$ npm install -g grunt-cli


Install dependencies
--------------------

Go to `src/main/gui` and invoke:

	$ npm install

Afterwards go to `src/main/gui/vendors/bootstrap` and run the same
command again to install the bootstrap dependencies too.


Build Stylesheets and Javascript
--------------------------------

Go to `src/main/gui` and invoke:

	$ grunt build
